WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.590 --> 00:00:02.620
[Immortal Samsara]
If one day...

2
00:00:02.620 --> 00:00:04.350
[Theme Song of Immortal Samsara]
[Sung by Zhang Jie and Zhang Liangying]

3
00:00:04.350 --> 00:00:05.500
I can see you again,

4
00:00:07.870 --> 00:00:09.340
will you be able to recognize me?

5
00:00:15.230 --> 00:00:15.800
I will.

6
00:00:33.790 --> 00:00:37.110
♪The most bitter memories
come from the frosty moon♪

7
00:00:37.430 --> 00:00:40.420
♪The dying years, lying on the ground♪

8
00:00:40.550 --> 00:00:43.680
♪To drown oneself in sorrow for one drop of tear♪

9
00:00:44.390 --> 00:00:47.200
♪Obsessed with forgetting♪

10
00:00:47.400 --> 00:00:50.660
♪To be oceans apart♪

11
00:00:50.850 --> 00:00:54.240
♪Until you turn around♪

12
00:00:54.440 --> 00:00:56.420
♪And think♪

13
00:00:56.480 --> 00:01:00.960
♪Of me♪

14
00:01:02.120 --> 00:01:05.380
♪The deepest affinity,
hidden within the darkness♪

15
00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:08.260
♪Love is all-embracing♪

16
00:01:08.580 --> 00:01:12.480
♪Loneliness marks me on my chest
with my longing for you♪

17
00:01:12.670 --> 00:01:15.490
♪Your clear eyes are like
the fragments of the moon♪

18
00:01:16.060 --> 00:01:18.620
♪Even after washing away the fine dust♪

19
00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:22.720
♪Your face is still imprinted in my mind♪

20
00:01:23.230 --> 00:01:24.900
♪As the cycle continues♪

21
00:01:25.090 --> 00:01:28.990
♪I lost my mind due to such longing♪

22
00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:33.470
♪You're an autumn breeze
in the bustling human world♪

23
00:01:33.790 --> 00:01:37.120
♪Forming a bed of flower petals♪

24
00:01:37.380 --> 00:01:40.000
♪Will you shed tears♪

25
00:01:40.260 --> 00:01:42.370
♪Over the truth of the mortal world?♪

26
00:01:43.460 --> 00:01:47.680
♪You're the unattainable autumn moon
high up in the sky♪

27
00:01:47.940 --> 00:01:50.820
♪Yet restrain your glow,
dare not to show your light♪

28
00:01:51.140 --> 00:01:57.020
♪Together with one's beloved in a dream♪

29
00:01:59.100 --> 00:02:00.620
[Bridge of Void]

30
00:02:12.730 --> 00:02:14.380
♪Our lives are short♪

31
00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:15.840
♪Yet we suffer for love♪

32
00:02:16.030 --> 00:02:18.840
♪People who yearn for love
bite off more than they can chew♪

33
00:02:19.740 --> 00:02:21.400
♪The night is barren♪

34
00:02:21.660 --> 00:02:22.500
♪As the night saw me♪

35
00:02:23.270 --> 00:02:25.900
♪My hatred is full to the brim♪

36
00:02:26.340 --> 00:02:29.540
♪As the wind blows and the flowers bloom♪

37
00:02:30.230 --> 00:02:33.360
♪I could not forget the things I was supposed to♪

38
00:02:34.070 --> 00:02:35.150
♪Not separating♪

39
00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:39.440
♪All the love birds♪

40
00:02:41.040 --> 00:02:42.450
♪Mistake weaves♪

41
00:02:42.770 --> 00:02:43.870
♪My love into a lie♪

42
00:02:44.320 --> 00:02:47.320
♪I leave, on the road, braving the wind and snow♪

43
00:02:47.960 --> 00:02:50.910
♪Fate has us spending
a thousand years missing each other♪

44
00:02:51.420 --> 00:02:54.360
♪Until the end of the world♪

45
00:02:54.780 --> 00:02:57.790
♪From now on, the ups and downs in our lives♪

46
00:02:58.300 --> 00:03:01.630
♪Are our companions♪

47
00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:07.010
♪Hoping that my ignorance
will be cured in my next life♪

48
00:03:08.420 --> 00:03:12.320
♪You're an autumn breeze
in the bustling human world♪

49
00:03:12.770 --> 00:03:15.970
♪Forming a bed of flower petals♪

50
00:03:16.160 --> 00:03:18.590
♪Will you shed tears♪

51
00:03:18.980 --> 00:03:21.090
♪Over the truth of the mortal world?♪

52
00:03:22.370 --> 00:03:26.460
♪You're the unattainable autumn moon
high up in the sky♪

53
00:03:26.910 --> 00:03:29.660
♪Yet restrain your glow,
dare not to show your light♪

54
00:03:30.240 --> 00:03:36.320
♪Together with one's beloved in a dream♪

55
00:03:41.640 --> 00:03:42.530
If there's a next life,

56
00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:46.050
I will never let go of you.

57
00:03:50.810 --> 00:03:51.770
♪After bidding you farewell♪

58
00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:54.840
♪The clouds above, the tiles below,
spring and fall♪

59
00:03:55.020 --> 00:03:57.850
♪Through the mountains and sea,
there's no place my heart can be♪

60
00:03:58.160 --> 00:04:03.800
♪No number of lifetimes will be enough
for our parting♪

61
00:04:04.850 --> 00:04:08.880
♪With the root of love still intact,
I saw a white-haired person on the shore♪

62
00:04:09.010 --> 00:04:12.210
♪We dare to visit the end of the world with our love♪

63
00:04:12.340 --> 00:04:18.680
♪To the human world at a splendid timing♪

64
00:04:19.399 --> 00:04:26.630
♪You and I will be together again
when the lotus blooms♪

65
00:04:31.430 --> 00:04:32.330
I truly didn't expect

66
00:04:33.990 --> 00:04:35.420
us to be together.

67
00:04:37.570 --> 00:04:38.340
This dream

68
00:04:39.810 --> 00:04:41.220
feels too great to be true.

